text: Rosenblad is a Swedish language surname, which mean "rose leaf". Notable people with the surname include: *Carl Rosenblad (equestrian) (1886–1953), Swedish equestrian *Carl Rosenblad (racing driver) (born 1969), Swedish auto racing driver *Mathias Rosenblad (1758–1847), Swedish politician Category:Swedish-language surnames
